1/ download elasticsearch

wget https://artifacts.elastic.co/downloads/elasticsearch/elasticsearch-7.13.1-linux-x86_64.tar.gz
( https://www.elastic.co/fr/downloads/elasticsearch )
extract

( docker single/multi node : https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/docker.html )

2/ Download cerebro

wget https://github.com/lmenezes/cerebro/releases/download/v0.9.4/cerebro-0.9.4.tgz
( https://github.com/lmenezes/cerebro/releases )
exract

3/ launch
cd elasticsearch-7.13.1
bin/elasticsearch

4/ cd cerebro
bin/cerebro

5/ open http://localhost:9000/#/rest?host=http:%2F%2Flocalhost:9200

6/ Create index 
PUT review

7/ add docs
POST /review/_doc/{id}